Squizzy::
She was cleaning up the lab and putting her tools away. She walked 
over to the remains of Beholder and Feline. She shuddered. Staying in 
a room with dead bots was not her idea of a good time. She grabbed a 
small lazar scalpal and removed the heads of both bots and put them 
in a small cryo-storage container. She then opened her link. "Zardus, 
what do you want me to do with the remains of these two bots. I have 
saved enough samples for future use."
